<i>We came out here for a job</i>
<i>that was supposed to take six weeks.</i>


215
00:11:16.862 --> 00:11:18.780
<i>It took six months,</i>
<i>that picture with Eddie Cantor</i>


216
00:11:18.864 --> 00:11:20.365
<i>called</i>Roman Scandals.

217
00:11:20.449 --> 00:11:24.244
<i>I had an absolutely wonderful association</i>
<i>with everyone at the studio.</i>


218
00:11:24.327 --> 00:11:25.996
<i>I loved Hollywood.</i>

219
00:11:26.079 --> 00:11:30.041
<i>I saw in it a place I wanted to live,</i>
<i>a place I wanted to bring my family.</i>


220
00:11:30.125 --> 00:11:32.252
<i>I had no thought of ever going back.</i>

221
00:11:32.335 --> 00:11:34.337
♪ ♪

222
00:11:38.508 --> 00:11:40.510
(audience laughter)

223
00:11:46.641 --> 00:11:48.685
What are you made up for, Lucy?

224
00:11:48.768 --> 00:11:52.147
Oh, darn it, you recognized me.

225
00:11:52.230 --> 00:11:53.773
(audience laughter)

226
00:11:53.857 --> 00:11:56.443
Well, if I hadn't worn this,
would you have known who it was?


227
00:11:56.526 --> 00:11:59.237
Of course.
What are you trying to prove?


228
00:11:59.321 --> 00:12:00.739
Well, I was just practicing.

229
00:12:00.822 --> 00:12:03.241
You know, us movie stars
have to go around disguised


230
00:12:03.325 --> 00:12:05.952
-or our fans will mob us.
-(laughs)


231
00:12:06.036 --> 00:12:09.456
Why, if it isn't Lucy Ricardo.

232
00:12:09.539 --> 00:12:11.166
Gee, can I have your autograph?

233
00:12:11.249 --> 00:12:13.043
Oh, Fred, don't be smart.

234
00:12:13.126 --> 00:12:14.252
Who's being smart?

235
00:12:14.336 --> 00:12:16.254
I want it on a check
for this month's rent.


236
00:12:16.338 --> 00:12:18.924
(audience laughter)

237
00:12:19.007 --> 00:12:21.009
You'll get your money, my good man.

238
00:12:21.092 --> 00:12:23.303
Us movie stars always pay our bills.

239
00:12:23.386 --> 00:12:24.888
(audience laughter)

240
00:12:24.971 --> 00:12:26.097
ETHEL:
Hey, wait a minute.


241
00:12:26.181 --> 00:12:28.099
I thought Ricky was gonna be the star.

242
00:12:28.183 --> 00:12:30.685
Oh, he'll be one, too. Don't worry.

